text:
This is why I really don't get the hate of other nctzens towards Tyong. Some solo stans keep on saying that he is selfish bc SM is always giving him the spotlight but they don't even appreciate how Tyong puts all the members as a priority. He keeps on hyping the members, doing his best to make them shine even in his little ways. It's always about the members when we hear him speak on interviews, and he wants everyone to have their own solo. His unreleased songs could already be an album if he likes, but he wants to focus on NCT as a group. Even before, we can already see how he cares for all the members and it's only good things that we hear about him. 

It is not easy to lead a 23-member group but Taeyong as he is, I know he'll do well. He is the best leader for NCT and those who think otherwise are blind about his leadership.
